{
  "name": "Frenzy Cackle",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Genjutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You collect and build all of your madness and instability and release it into an echoing wave that tears through the minds of creatures within range.</p><p>All creatures, including yourself, in range must make an Intelligence saving throw. You make your saving throw at advantage.</p><p>Critical Success: Affected creature is able to resist this jutsu's effects.</p><p>Success: Affected creature becomes blinded until the end of the current turn as their madness blinds them.</p><p>Failure: Affected creatures takes 4d12 psychic damage and becomes blinded for the next minute, remaking saving throws at the end of each of their turns, ending this jutsu's effect on a success.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creatures takes 6d12 psychic damage and becomes blinded, deafened, and incapable of smelling or tasting as they begin to laugh manically for the next minute, remaking their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, with a 1d4 penalty ending this jutsu's effect on a success.</p>",
